Package com.cyc.query.client.explanations Description

Provides the classes specific to working with QueryAnswerExplanations, and specifically for ProofViews. QueryAnswerExplanations can be generated from QuestionAnswers, and then either exported or manipulated in Java.
See Also:
QueryAnswer, QueryAnswerExplanation, ProofView
